name: Psilocibios 0005
description:
Ektachrome slideshow with virtual reality treatment reproduced in 2-D with Terence Mckenna's voice in the background.

Author's note: This work was presented in my room today 7-10-2021 for myself, while listening to Terrence Mckenna in the background: OPENING THE DOORS OF CREATIVITY https://youtu.be/R7tEDQFi7Po
